Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴托奇亚共和国
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.83,0:00:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,位于天特拉地区的茂密森林中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.04,0:00:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一座海拔3722米的死火山 枯枯戮山上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一处以暗杀家族有名的揍敌客家宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了一睹那神秘的宅邸 前来参观的游客络绎不绝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里由此成为了这个国家的旅游胜地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.86,0:01:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你们想在这儿呆多长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.13,0:02:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见到奇犽之前 在那之前绝不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\bord0\c&H000000&\pos(960,956.25)\fscy120}门卫{\c&H0148F9&} × {\c&H000000&\fscy120}的{\c&H0148F9&} × {\c&H000000&\fscy120}责任
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了见到奇犽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.03,0:02:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杰一行人眼前有一个必须跨越的障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的前方 究竟有什么在等待着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.49,0:02:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们雇佣工的住所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.56,0:02:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天已经太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先住一晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.32,0:02:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得有客人来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫席克安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一样是这里的雇佣工
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能被皆卜罗赏识 挺了不起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请自便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过在这种地方你们也轻松不了就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来见奇犽少爷?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也太滑稽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我们可是很认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你们个忠告 劝你们早点放弃 赶紧回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.10,0:03:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该听皆卜罗说过「试炼之门」了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这里是什么地方 想必你也心知肚明了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我们无法轻易到达那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不会回去的 直到见到奇犽为止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在奇犽最痛苦的时候 没能陪伴在他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候 如果我在奇犽身边的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定就能阻止他了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇犽是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 要不就在这儿先进行特训吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特训?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 皆卜罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听好了 小杰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个门即使是三个人合力 只要能打开就算OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间虽然短 但只要努力锻炼也不是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不愿意被试探
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果只有这条路的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能试一试了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 有样东西想让你们先穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 这也忒重吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个有50公斤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除睡觉时间 请时刻穿着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦适应了 还会增加重量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 请喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个茶杯20公斤重 壶有40公斤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个房间里 所有家具和餐具都有20公斤以上的重量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 这就是特训啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正过个两三天就会叫苦连天了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,席克安 交班时间早就过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 他并没有恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 厕所在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那扇门后面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非 那扇门...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 那个也有500公斤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,500...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧 憋不住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯特 开门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇犽 你有好好反省吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用啊 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子根本没有反省
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得再狠狠地抽打一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糜稽 你给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.09,0:07:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇犽 只要别倔着 说句「我反省了」就好了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一说 听说你有个叫小杰的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.79,0:07:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真不知好歹 竟来挑战「试炼之门」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杰 来了...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糜稽 你又多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊 奇犽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们竟然没告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.18,0:07:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拿什么口气和妈妈说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都叫你闭嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我觉得没必要和你说啊 奇犽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是不可能打开那扇门的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能打开的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杰的话 能打开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 即使能把门推开了 也不可能到达这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杰 他一定会来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定会来到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 小杰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是来见习的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼下最重要的是先治好你的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我和酷拉皮卡来开就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 酷拉皮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说肯定不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 还是纹丝不动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 才特训没多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要尽全力 总能成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 头脑简单的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说了 无论你们怎么做都是白费功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该有自知之明了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.28,0:10:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你是这么觉得的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就眼不见为净 乖乖去干自己的活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杰是我们的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙伴要去见他重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们全力相助是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞 再试一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 光用蛮力是推不开的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要看准时机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须尽最大力气同时压在两扇门上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样门才能打开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看准时机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽最大力气 同时压在两扇门上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.18,0:11:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.36,0:11:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷欧力 酷拉皮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于推动了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(600,333)\bord3.375\c&H030301&\3c&HDEF0F5&}Hunter语 讲解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(500,0)\pos(637.333,1048.5)\bord0\shad9\c&H080502&\4c&H73A6D2&}试炼之门
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试炼之门...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是...目前为止没什么特别举动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依旧是那么冰冷的语气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两人 今天就把那马甲脱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢天谢地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱下马甲 一定能打开门了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啦 酷拉皮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:12:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能推的再开了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加把劲 雷欧力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杰 你干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的左手...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系了 已经恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恢复了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 小杰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那个 要配合呼吸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 推吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能打开...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了啊 小杰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺着道往到那座山走去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宅邸就在山里的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来有点难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.97,0:14:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这儿工作20年 都还没去过那座山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮不上忙 不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆卜罗伯伯 席克安大哥 多谢相助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:14:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的话 能到底宅邸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 那是通向地狱之路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是因为三年前的那件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被一个见习管家弄得全军覆灭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想就觉得背后发凉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人总要有自知之明的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你很有自知之明 来这里工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失言了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个地方 无论是雇主还是雇佣工全是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦越过那里就...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.44,0:15:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「试炼之门」打开了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇犽现在处于非常时期
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准任何人靠近他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更别说什么朋友这些无用之物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你们在私有地内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未经允许 不准通过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都打过电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是从「试炼之门」进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但管家中心没有允许你们进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎样才能得到许可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是朋友也行不通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 没有许可的先例
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底只能强行进入咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 你们只能走到这儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦越过这条线 我将以武力驱逐你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杰 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷欧力 酷拉皮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准出手 交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们无心与你交手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是来见见奇犽而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论什么理由都没用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是遵从雇主的命令而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.36,0:18:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试几次都没用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会让你们通过的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要过去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要见奇犽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎您回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇犽少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该知道这样是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也快阻止他啊 是朋友...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 只是来见朋友而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是来见奇犽而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 必须却得这么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 我已经踏进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不打我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和米凯不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:34.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎样隐藏自己的感情 依然有人类的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在念到奇犽的名字的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只是一瞬间 你的目光却变柔和了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.26,0:20:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇犽少...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区下人 还真是口无遮拦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛是我们在虐待奇犽一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是个见习生而已 太放肆了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.31,0:21:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是小杰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.80,0:21:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听伊路米说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要过来的事 奇犽也知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我来替他传口信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.38,0:21:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢你们能来 我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在我不能见你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.72,0:21:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.16,0:21:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于进入邸内的小杰他们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却有一堵墙挡住了他们的去路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我不能见你们」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这句来自奇犽悲伤的传话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.71,0:23:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 揍敌客 × 的 × 家族
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.29,0:23:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你来说 奇犽是怎样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
